[package]

edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = []
keywords = []
categories = []
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
env_logger = "0.9"
html_parser = "*"
json = "*"
log = "0.4.1"
serde_json = "*"
toml = "0.5"
tracing-subscriber = "0.2"

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.11.9"
features = ["default-tls"]
optional = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "*"
features = ["derive"]
optional = false

[dependencies.serenity]
version = "0.10.10"
features = ["utils", "cache", "framework", "standard_framework", "rustls_backend"]
optional = false

[dependencies.solanabeach]
path = "./src/solana_helper/solanabeach"
features = []
optional = false

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.0.0"
features = ["full"]
optional = false

bin = []
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[package]
name = "solanabeach"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
authors = []
keywords = []
categories = []

autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
log = "*"
serde = "*"
serde_json = "*"

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "*"
features = ["default-tls"]
